BEGIN:VCALENDAR
PRODID:-//notapattern//calendar export 1.0//EN
VERSION:2.0
CALSCALE:GREGORIAN
METHOD:PUBLISH
X-WR-CALNAME:Buena Vista Social Club
X-WR-TIMEZONE:America/New_York
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:980171
DTSTAMP:20260314T205843Z
DTSTART:20260314T233000Z
DTEND:20260315T014000Z
SUMMARY:Buena Vista Social Club
LOCATION:Gerald Schoenfeld Theatre, 236 West 45th Street, New York NY 10036
DESCRIPTION:<p>Winner! 5 Tony Awards&reg;<br /><br />Step into the heart
  of Cuba, beyond the glitz of the Tropicana, to a place where blazing
  trumpets and sizzling guitars set the dance floor on fire. Here, the real
  sound of Havana is born&mdash;and one woman discovers the music that will
  change her life forever.<br /><br />Inspired by true events, the new
  Broadway musical <em>Buena Vista Social Club</em>&trade; brings the
  Grammy&reg; Award-winning album to thrilling life&mdash;and tells the
  story of the legends who lived it. A world-class band joins a sensational
  cast of musicians, actors, and dancers from across the globe for an
  authentic experience unlike any you've seen or heard before. Don't miss
  this captivating tale of big dreams, second chances, and the unbreakable
  bonds of making music together.<br /><br />&ldquo;Give yourself over to
  <em>Buena Vista Social Club</em>.&rdquo; (<em>Time Out New York</em>)</p>
END:VEVENT
